<h2>Dissolution of Marriage</h2>
<p>Unlike many other states, here in the State of Florida, a spouse does not need grounds for divorce in order to file
    for dissolution of marriage. However, the spouse must be a current state resident who has resided in the state for
    at least six consecutive months. </p>
<h2>Simple Divorce</h2>
<p>One of the most frequently asked questions concerning a divorce or dissolution of marriage is whether they need a
